Vienna To-Do File
=================

Update this file with a list of things that users have requested but which aren't yet implemented.
Thanks!

(Items marked 2.1 are currently scheduled for a post 2.0 release unless I can be convinced otherwise).

Wishlist Items
==============
- Bloglines integration. (2.1)
- Purge old articles.
- Auto-discover feeds if subscription URL is to a web page.
- Sort on multiple columns.
- Per-folder sorting. (2.1)
- Semi-transparent main window when not in front. (2.1)
- Show the feed icon in the article list pane. (2.1)
- Download files directly from Vienna. (2.1)
- Support retrieving RSS 2.0 comments. (2.1)
- Spotlight support. (2.1)
- Export groups vs. flat export.

Coding To-Do Items
==================
- Rewrite ParseXmlDate in XMLParser.m to eliminate CUrl dependency.
- Renaming a folder does not update the folder name in smart folders that reference it.
